text: Was very pleased with my experience in this branch. Came on a Saturday morning. There were DBS staff waiting at the entrance and were quick to help with getting the correct queue number. I was served by Fleurdelyn who was extremely efficient, helpful and personable. Very happy with the service.
The staff (Masshita) was extremely kind and helpful to guide me to do the complicated online transactions with her iPad. She is always smiling and provides good customer services.Thanks!

Served by Mira. Was expecting a long wait for opening account, but done in 20ish minutes. Exceeded expectation by a long mile. Very friendly and knowledgeable officer. Seriously not sure what the low rating is all about, come see for yourself.

Massiha (sorry if I spelled wrongly) was on the ball and knowledgeable, she was able to assist without me having to take a queue number:) Really appreciate you helping my helper out w her ibanking and card activation!

Came in at an off-peak hour and they also had off-peak no. of staff (4) behind the counters with a turnover of only 2 customers
per 25 mins across all four counters.
